write() - Method in class read.DictMaker
creates a new file with the name "medialab/hangman_DICTIONARY-" + this.ID_dict + ".txt" or over-writes it if it already exists
writes all the current words (each one in a separate line)
or prints the exception and returns if an exception occurs
